00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:09,240
and different kinds of creatures that have different degrees of competency

712
00:44:09,240 --> 00:44:10,840
to reach various goals.

713
00:44:10,840 --> 00:44:12,520
So let's talk about this then.

714
00:44:12,520 --> 00:44:14,360
If that's the definition of intelligence,

715
00:44:15,160 --> 00:44:19,000
let's ask what kind of collective intelligence do these cellular swarms deploy?

716
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:23,560
I've made this argument that the cells of the body making in embryo

