00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:39,960
They have a specific ability to adapt to perturbations.

723
00:44:39,960 --> 00:44:42,200
That's more than simple emergence.

724
00:44:42,200 --> 00:44:43,800
And let me show you some examples.

725
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:50,840
So development is quite reliable and has the ability to reach the specific region

726
00:44:50,840 --> 00:44:55,560
of the anatomical amorphous space, meaning the various different configurations

727
00:44:55,560 --> 00:44:58,040
that a body might have to go from here to here.

