00:44:58,040 --> 00:45:02,760
So you go from a single cell and then two cells to a whole body.

729
00:45:02,760 --> 00:45:07,240
But the amazing thing is that if you cut this embryo in half,

730
00:45:07,240 --> 00:45:09,160
