733
00:45:14,840 --> 00:45:19,640
In the face of this massive perturbation, it is able to still get to where it's going.

734
00:45:19,640 --> 00:45:23,400
So if you boil everything down to two dimensions, just for sake of illustration,

735
00:45:23,400 --> 00:45:27,320
the normal embryo does this, but the embryo cut in half,

736
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:29,480
which is in a different location in that space,

737
00:45:29,480 --> 00:45:31,480
actually is able to get to where it needs to go.

