00:45:41,480 --> 00:45:44,840
And there are local maxima that can be avoided and so on.

742
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:49,320
So being able to navigate to the same region from different starting conditions

743
00:45:49,320 --> 00:45:53,880
is a kind of intelligence that we view as navigation.

