00:46:00,840 --> 00:46:06,360
This guy regenerates his limbs, his eyes, jaws, portions of the heart and brain,

748
00:46:06,360 --> 00:46:09,720
spinal cord, ovaries, amazingly regenerative.

749
00:46:09,720 --> 00:46:14,600
What happens is that when a limb is amputated and they bite each other's legs off all the time

750
00:46:14,600 --> 00:46:15,800
when they're when they're housed together.

751
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:20,440
So this is a natural experiment that happens, whether it's here or here or up here,

