00:46:23,480 --> 00:46:26,920
And they make a standard salamander leg and then they stop.

754
00:46:26,920 --> 00:46:31,320
That's the most amazing part of regeneration that first of all,

755
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:34,680
that it happens exactly the same way no matter what, where you start from.

