00:47:07,400 --> 00:47:10,920
So below a certain age, they will have a cosmetically very, very nice

769
00:47:10,920 --> 00:47:13,240
regeneration of a fingertip amputation.

770
00:47:13,240 --> 00:47:18,200
And deer are a large adult mammal that regenerates a centimeter and a half

