00:47:18,200 --> 00:47:20,360
of new bone per day when they're growing this.

772
00:47:20,360 --> 00:47:24,680
So bone, vasculature, innervation, skin, all of it.

773
00:47:24,680 --> 00:47:28,280
So this ability, and in fact, in the correct pattern.

