00:50:31,560 --> 00:50:36,040
And what we found is that even those animals generally make pretty normal frogs.

835
00:50:36,040 --> 00:50:40,360
Because all of these organs move in novel unnatural paths

836
00:50:40,360 --> 00:50:42,520
to get to where they're going and then they stop.

